{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in the exciting whirlwind of events that happen to a reclusive gamer. Learn to travel between worlds. Help your new companion, an unusual cat, get rid of the curse.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Parallel World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597800/extras/battles_short.gif?t=1737989159\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Become an adventurer, conquering a fickle dungeon full of enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Defeat all the bosses, thereby removing the curse from the magician in the body of a cat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Find and master all the weapons and abilities hidden in the depths of the dungeon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Meet the inhabitants of the parallel world and learn the history each</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Real World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597800/extras/home_short.gif?t=1737989159\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embellish your home, turning it from a hovel into a comfortable home</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Create items, cook food, brew potions and much more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Find out the secrets of your home, the history of past residents</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Travel to different locations in search of ingredients and clues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Sleep, eat, play, wash, go to the toilet and etc.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The entire gameplay will be brightened up by a variety of mini-games that perform various functions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam